text:
The document at http://logging.apache.org/log4j/docs/documentation.html has
several broken links in the 'Log4j presentations' section.

  * http://www.jug-l.org/log4j.html (Advanced Log4j) : No log4j document at that
url.
  * https://www.qos.ch/ac2001/F11-10.html (Log4j, a logging package for the Java
language) : 404
  * http://www.ejug.org/OpenSource%20Log4j2_files/frame.htm (Log4j presentation
by the) : 404
creator: lparra@itboss.com.ar
carnold@apache.org
text:
jug-l.org and ejug.org have apparently let their domains lapsed.  The links have
been removed.  The ApacheCon 2001 presentation is still available at qos.ch but
using http, not https.  Fixed in rev 427699.
